data.description: Beautiful 3/2.5 townhome- new tile and carpet. Kitchen all stainless steel appliances. Smart technology includes Nest thermostat and Ring doorbell. Use of amenities in the Watermill subdivision across the street- annual fee of $515 in addition to monthly HOA. Close and convenient to shopping, 295 and First Coast Expressway. Property will be sold AS-IS. Happy Showing!
